                <h2>About Stock Tracker</h2>
                <p>Our Stock Tracker application will alow you to enter stock information to allow you to track performance of your portfolio. We allow you to enter the number of shares you won, your stock price, dividend yield, and more.</p>
                <p>In addition to tracking your information on our website, our team has integrated the stock tracker information with a mobile app so you may track your information on the go. Currently, the mobile is available on Android and iPhone mobile devices.</p>
